name: N911Request
title: 911 Request
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set includes responses that stemmed from 911 requests.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this value set is to identify patients who received care during an EMS response in which the request was received via 911 services. Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element would map to the Communicationcategory.),(Inclusion Criteria: Include EMS encounters that were initiated via 911 request, including calls, responses, and dispatches.),(Exclusion Criteria: None)
